import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import CardGroup from 'react-bootstrap/CardGroup';
import { Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';


    function GroupExample() {
      return (
        <CardGroup>

            <Row>
                <Col>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
                    <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Cadastro de Formula</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                    </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                    <Card.Footer>
                    <small className="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
                    </Card.Footer>
                </Card>
                </Col>
                <Col>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
                    <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>A Produzir </Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                        Material a Produzir...
                    </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                    <Card.Footer>
                    <small className="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
                    </Card.Footer>
                </Card>
                </Col>
                <Col>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
                    <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Produzido</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                        Material Produzido
                    </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                    <Card.Footer>
                    <small className="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
                    </Card.Footer>
                </Card>
                </Col>
            </Row>
                        
            <Row>
            <Col>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
                    <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Batelada</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                        Batelada...
                    </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                    <Card.Footer>
                    <small className="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
                    </Card.Footer>
                </Card>
            </Col>

            <Col>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
                    <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Silos</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                        Silos
                    </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                    <Card.Footer>
                    <small className="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
                    </Card.Footer>
                </Card>
            </Col>

            <Col>
                <Card>
                    <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px160" />
                    <Card.Body>
                    <Card.Title>Reservado</Card.Title>
                    <Card.Text>
                        Reserva
                    </Card.Text>
                    </Card.Body>
                    <Card.Footer>
                    <small className="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
                    </Card.Footer>
                </Card>
            </Col>
            </Row>
        </CardGroup>
      );
    }
    
    export default GroupExample;
